# Visual-asset generation workspace
# Tape files, mock demo provider, canned response JSON, and scratch vhs
# output all live under .vhs-work/. Only the finished assets/*.gif files
# get committed to the repo — the generation code stays local so we
# don't pollute little-coder's published surface with recording tooling.
.vhs-work/